parsed.explanation: Several structural and encoding errors were fixed. Encoding errors related to historical German text/OCR issues (e.g., 'Brandmüllerischen', 'verständigen', 'Hauß-Patter', 'adelichem', 'neu', 'französischen') were corrected. Structural corrections focused primarily on the first book citation, where the <AUTHOR> tag was incorrectly nested within a split <TITLE> tag, which was resolved by merging the title parts and placing the author tag as a sibling element within <BIBL>. Furthermore, missing <BIBL> opening and closing tags were added for the third entry (Fleury's Kirchen-Historien).
